reviewText: Loretta LaRoche is funny - the quality of this dvd is poor.
I love Loretta LaRoche's work. She's SO right - we take way too many things way too seriously!

This was recommended to me by a teacher who was teaching a class about using humor in the classroom. I got it and love it!! It is hilarious! My sister sat around one night and watched it and laughed all the way through it.
This product was a gift for a family member.  They enjoyed the product alot. This is a great product and I recommend it.

My Doctor told me the that I needed to get rid of the stress in my life.  It would help me to fight my disease.
Watching this really helps me put things in perspective.
She is right!  Live is not a stress rehearsl!
